headline: Labcorp Announces Acquisition of Select Assets of BioReference Health's Innovative Oncology and Related Clinical Testing Services Businesses
summary: Labcorp (NYSE: LH), a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, and OPKO Health, Inc. (Nasdaq: OPK), a multinational biopharmaceutical and diagnostics company, announced today that they have entered into an agreement for Labcorp to acquire select assets of BioReference Health, a wholly owned subsidiary of OPKO Health.
